data.description: Lovely Place to call HOME!  Nestled in the quiet community of Silver Pines, is this single story updated MUST SEE house.  Special details:  Office w/ french doors,  formal dining w/ wood floors, large living area w/ beautiful custom tile flooring, updated kitchen w/ granite counters and subway tile backsplash, oversized primary bedroom with en-suite bath (shower w/ tile & accent inlay plus frameless shower doors). Two secondary bedrooms and full bath off main hallway. Carpet and memory foam pad in bedrooms.  Updated fixtures throughout. Washer/Dryer and Refrigerator stay with the house.  Rain Sprinkler System installed in 2021. The house is also wired for an alarm system. Lots to love about this house!
